// TOTAL MEASURES IN THIS FILE: 45+
// 
// REMAINING MEASURES (in separate files):
//   02_Advanced_DAX_Measures.dax — Ranking, Pareto, ABC, Forecasting
//   03_Field_Parameters.dax — Dynamic dimension/measure switching
//   04_Calculation_Groups.dax — Time intelligence calculation groups
//
// HOW TO ADD TO POWER BI:
//   1. Open Power BI Desktop with RetailDW model
//   2. Select "FactSales" table in Fields pane
//   3. Click "New Measure" 
//   4. Paste any formula above
//   5. Press Enter → Measure appears in model
//   6. Drag to a visual → See the result!
//
// PRO TIP: Create a "Measures" table (empty table) to organize all measures
//   Modeling tab → New Table → Measures = ROW("x", BLANK())
//   Then move all measures to this table for clean organization
// =============================================================================
